data.description: This beautiful home offers tons of privacy and more than enough space inside and outside. Sitting on 8 plus acres, this home will allow you to let your imagination run free. Stunning views surround this home. There is also a pond located behind the home where you can fish on your free time. Three bedrooms, 2 baths are located on the first floor with the bonus room located upstairs. Enjoy the cozy fireplace in the vaulted great room or even breakfast overlooking the pond. This home has so much to offer. There is also an old barn on site that would make an amazing workshop. Greenhouse, 2 wells on the property, an emergency generator, two 100 gallon propane tanks,  and so much more. New appliances in the kitchen will convey as well. MOTIVATED!!
